Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the bowling alley where fun never stops. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm trying to figure out a billing issue I have on my latest invoice.

I'd be happy to help with that. Could I start by getting your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Can you please provide your account number? It's typically eight digits long.

Of course, it's one two three four five six seven eight.

Great, thanks Jamie. Could you also let me know the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account for verification?

Yes, the last four digits are nine eight seven six.

Perfect, I've got your account pulled up here. I see the billing discrepancy now, and it looks like there was a duplicate charge. I'll get that corrected immediately.

Thanks, Alex! I appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Jamie. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that's all for now. Thanks again!

Alright. Thank you for your patience, Jamie. Have a wonderful day! Goodbye!
